out creating seamless user experiences as much as building performant systems.Curious and empathetic: Driven to use technology to solve real people\u2019s problems.How You\u2019ll Make a DifferenceBuild end-to-end solutions: Design, implement, and maintain scalable, secure, and high-performance applications across the stack.Create exceptional front-end experiences: Develop rich, accessible, and responsive interfaces that make financial management simple, transparent, and trustworthy.Power our backend ecosystem: Own and develop backend services and APIs, from authentication to banking and compliance integrations.Collaborate across teams: Work closely with product, design, and operations to turn user needs into technical solutions that have real impact.Elevate engineering standards: Drive improvements in code quality, developer experience, and system reliability.Balance speed with rigor: Iterate quickly while ensuring our systems meet the standards of a regulated fintech environment.Champion best practices: Lead the way in testing, observability, and deployment for full-stack systems.nsave ValuesAlongside technical excellence, we look for people whose values align with ours:Service - \u201cMission First\u201d: We put the mission, our customers, and our team above self.Urgency - \u201cStay focused. Move fast\u201d: We act with urgency and intention, concentrating on what matters most.Ownership - \u201cAct as an Owner\u201d: We take responsibility for outcomes end-to-end.Standards - \u201cPursue Excellence\u201d: We hold ourselves to high personal standards and continuously improve.Please apply only if you:Are deeply motivated by nsave\u2019s mission and the problems we are solvingThrive in high-ownership, high-accountability environmentsAre comfortable operating with urgency and ambiguityWant to build from first principles in an early-stage, high-growth companyEmployee Benefitsnsave Share Options (subject to eligibility and plan rules)25 days Annual leave (+ UK Public Holidays)Visa Sponsorship available\u00a0Private Medical InsuranceFree monthly Gym membership (via hussle)\u00a3500 GBP Health & Wellness BudgetIndividual Learning & Development BudgetSeason Ticket Loan SchemeCycle to Work Schemensave is an equal opportunity employer. We are committed to creating a diverse and inclusive workplace and welcome applications from all backgrounds, identities, and experiences. We do not discriminate on the basis of age, gender, ethnicity, religion, sexual orientation, disability, or any other protected characteristic.\n\nBegin your response with {\n", "v15_labels": {"loc_raw": "London, England, United Kingdom", "loc": "IN_LONDON", "arr_raw": "Full-time, on-site role based in London (Shoreditch)", "arr": "IN_OFFICE", "sen_raw": "Full-Stack Engineer", "sen": "LEVEL_2", "tech_raw": "TypeScript, React Native, NestJS (Node.js), Postgres, AWS (ECS, RDS/Postgres), Docker, Kafka", "tech": ["NODE", "REACT", "JS_TS"], "comp_raw": null, "comp": "NO_GBP"}}
