oftware Engineer", "sen": "LEVEL_3", "tech_raw": "AI, full-stack, continuous deployment, licensing systems", "tech": ["AI_ML"], "comp_raw": "For this role, the estimated base salary range is between $176,000 - $200,000 CAD.", "comp": "NO_GBP"}}
